data.description: What a beauty! Welcome to 158 Forest Bluff Dr. situated in a cul-de-sac on 2.8 acres!  This 3 bed 3 bath. home lots to offer. Complete with a large combo kitchen with abundant cabinet, counter space and island with plenty of room for  your friends and family to enjoy, and completely open to the family room as well! Upstairs you will find all 3 bedrooms including the large bonus room you can use as an addition family room, office, etc.. the options are endless! Schedule your showing today! Seller offering $5,000 in Concessions and Home Warranty to Buyer.
